<h2><strong><span style="font-size:17pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Method 1: Download Videos Directly from the Telegram App</span></strong></h2>
<p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Telegram provides a built-in feature for downloading videos directly to your device. Here&rsquo;s how you can do it:</span></p>
<h3><strong><span style="font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Steps for Mobile Users (iOS/Android):</span></strong></h3>
<ol>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Open Telegram</span></strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">&nbsp;and navigate to the chat containing the video.</span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Locate the video you want to download. Tap on it to open.</span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Tap the&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">download icon</span></strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">&nbsp;(usually a downward arrow) visible on the video.</span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Wait for the download to complete. The video will now be available in your device&rsquo;s gallery or file manager.</span></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<h3><strong><span style="font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Steps for Desktop Users (Windows/Mac):</span></strong></h3>
<ol>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Open the Telegram desktop app and locate the chat with the video.</span></p>
    </li>
    <li style="list-style-type:decimal;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
        <p><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">Hover over the video and click the&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">download icon</span></strong><span style="font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">.</span></p>
